1. *šala* je najbolji način da se neko nasmije. (A joke is the best way to make someone laugh.)
2. *Šala* je bila toliko smiješna da je svi smijali. (The joke was so funny that everyone was laughing.)
3. On je imao odličnu *šalu* za reći. (He had a great joke to tell.)
4. Ona je bila vrlo dobra u *šalama*. (She was very good at jokes.)
5. Oni su najčešće provodili vrijeme razgovarajući i *šalama*. (They usually spent time talking and joking.)